Contract Liabilities
Amounts received from certain bottlers/distributors at inception of their distribution contracts or
at the inception of certain sales/marketing programs are accounted for as deferred revenue. As of
December 31, 2022 and 2021, the Company had $267.1 million and $285.8 million of deferred revenue,
